metadata.name: Celestial
metadata.description: Celestial presents a surreal dreamscape, with a mirror floating at the center of the room, reflecting the celestial gardens of dreams. The light pink clouds and off-white sky create a serene ambiance that evokes a sense of calm and peacefulness. The celestial gardens offer a sense of otherworldliness, blurring the boundary between the digital and the physical world, leaving the feeling of an untouchingly tangible perception of reality.
